1.0.name: wordpress/simple-social-sharing
1.0.description:
NOTE This plugin is no longer supported and will not be receiving any updates. Due to the ever changing nature of how the various social networks require sharing mechanisms, there are other plugins better suited to keep up with it.

A simple single post footer to include sharing links for your visitors.
